originalText.text: Dr. Santoyo is both extremely knowledgeable and skilled. I asked many pointed and general questions during visits, in labor and delivery and postpartum. She was able to explain everything I wanted, and needed, to know. She went above and beyond when delivering my third child. I will be forever grateful.

originalText.text:
Dr. Santoyo was great. It was my first time seeing her, so I was nervous, but her bedside manner was fantastic.
She took the time to explain things to me without judgement and always asked consent before moving to the next part of the exam. Seems like the bare minimum, but it often isn’t the case in many practices. Glad I found a new doctor I trust!

originalText.text: The practice is friendly and efficient and I love Dr. Santoyo. She is kind, highly intelligent, solutions-oriented and calls you back in a timely fashion if you have an issue.  For me this  is huge in today's  medical world (which tends to be an impersonal black hole.) I trust her and feel very lucky to have found her.
